# MoonPad — Meteora DAMM v2 Integration (Replaces Raydium Sections)

## Why DAMM v2 and What Changes

This document replaces the Raydium CPI sections in `anchor-program-spec.md` and
`platform-fullstack-spec.md`. Everything else in those documents stays the same.

