## Updated Anchor Program: `launch_presale` Instruction

Replace the entire Raydium CPI section with the following.

### What the launch does

1. Wrap 85 SOL from the vault into WSOL
2. Call DAMM v2 `initialize_customizable_pool` — creates pool + position NFT
3. Call DAMM v2 `permanent_lock_position` — locks liquidity forever (rug-proof)
4. Store the position NFT pubkey in `presale_state` so fees can be claimed later
5. Set `tokens_per_lamport_x64` for distribution, set `launched = true`
6. Transfer 50% of tokens to token_vault for contributors to claim (same as before)

